    "description": "<p>Nexia Singapore PAC. Our directors and managers have extensive experience and are supported by a large group of dedicated and skilled professional staff. Our expertise covers&nbsp;audit and assurance,&nbsp;tax,&nbsp;business advisory,&nbsp;outsourcing,&nbsp;risk and governance,&nbsp;corporate recovery,&nbsp;company incorporation,&nbsp;corporate secretarial services, and&nbsp;IT infrastructure and solutions.&nbsp;Combined with our global network, our capabilities and resources allow us to provide you the support that your business needs, no matter where you are on your growth journey.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At Nexia Singapore PAC, we constantly strive to deliver service excellence.&nbsp;Regardless of the nature or size of the engagement, we insist on uncompromising quality, working in our clients’ best interests while upholding our values of integrity and professionalism.&nbsp;We aspire to be a practice that clients and employees are proud to be associated with.</p>",
